          <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
            <p class="flex-auto">It doesn't matter if you want to loose weight, gain muscle, or just be more focused and productive. We make sure that your meals hit your macro and calorie goals.</p>
            <p class="mt-6">
            </p>
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6 flex-none text-sky-600">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12 2.25c-5.385 0-9.75 4.365-9.75 9.75s4.365 9.75 9.75 9.75 9.75-4.365 9.75-9.75S17.385 2.25 12 2.25zM12.75 6a.75.75 0 00-1.5 0v6c0 .414.336.75.75.75h4.5a.75.75 0 000-1.5h-3.75V6z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            Save time
          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
            <p class="flex-auto">No need to think about where or what to eat. Good food just shows up at your door step. No effort required on your side.</p>
            <p class="mt-6">
            </p>
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col">
          <dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6 flex-none text-sky-600">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M20.599 1.5c-.376 0-.743.111-1.055.32l-5.08 3.385a18.747 18.747 0 00-3.471 2.987 10.04 10.04 0 014.815 4.815 18.748 18.748 0 002.987-3.472l3.386-5.079A1.902 1.902 0 0020.599 1.5zm-8.3 14.025a18.76 18.76 0 001.896-1.207 8.026 8.026 0 00-4.513-4.513A18.75 18.75 0 008.475 11.7l-.278.5a5.26 5.26 0 013.601 3.602l.502-.278zM6.75 13.5A3.75 3.75 0 003 17.25a1.5 1.5 0 01-1.601 1.497.75.75 0 00-.7 1.123 5.25 5.25 0 009.8-2.62 3.75 3.75 0 00-3.75-3.75z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            Customized
          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
            <p class="flex-auto">The meals are based on your preferences and goals. We get better over time and deliver the food you like consistently. And if you don't like your dish for the day, just mix it up.</p>
            <p class="mt-6">
            </p>
          </dd>
        </div>
